Class StreetViewLayout

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxmaps.StreetViewLayout

  • public class StreetViewLayout
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents layout of street view. These options provides possibility to customize position and size of StreetViewPanorama object.
